<ul>
  <li><strong>Fundamental Instructions</strong> - OpCodes are the basic building blocks that enable Programmable Transactions on Kaspa</li>
  <li><strong>Stack-Based Execution</strong> - All OpCode operations work through a deterministic stack-based virtual machine</li>
  <li><strong>Conditional Logic</strong> - Control flow OpCodes enable complex decision-making within transaction scripts</li>
  <li><strong>Extensible Design</strong> - New OpCodes can be added through protocol upgrades to enhance functionality</li>
  <li><strong>Smart Contract Foundation</strong> - OpCodes provide the foundation for advanced financial applications and covenant-like behavior</li>
</ul>
